{"tid":2406822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老味，邊條撚屌喺筲箕灣到放煙花啊？","createTime":"2021-02-13T14:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T16:39:19.000Z","uid":119902,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85267ad7374da9a5f4cbddc4458166ed2d853ca5","tid":2406822,"uid":119902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，我沖緊涼都走撚左出黎，以為邊到爆炸啊<br />\n<br />\n仆街，係未筲箕灣好撚似元朗咁，獨立左啊？<br />\n<br />\n光復耀東，煙花革命，係未咁玩先？"},{"pid":"fa65a8acc2e1bc2d36323f459c6985618f7a68b9","tid":2406822,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"皇軍宣示筲箕灣主權姐，無人投訴即係同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa48b5d73e9dddf2bbc3c64c7558b442f1e8571c","tid":2406822,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"點解有炸藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10144357a83ebab9ae69571d8514e1f4a99a514f","tid":2406822,"uid":174829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01159c86ab24000fa2a89fb60253b3a9b39b4b5","tid":2406822,"uid":224103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9364328ed53933205db5b023d3f7bea4ba47c8a","tid":2406822,"uid":119902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"班狗日撚日鳩打稻草人，成日唔知邊到搵D炸藥，然後講乜野恐怖主義<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地班警嫂啊，而家有條仆街，真係攞D炸藥啊，做狗既你地應該聞撚到個喎，人呢？契弟<br />\n<br />\n我做街坊既真係驁，你地幻想出黎既恐怖分子，會唔會起筲箕灣狗署門口到，日撚日放煙花，為你地吶喊助威架？"},{"pid":"0a74c0476f727b314fbe37b190859560230aeab0","tid":2406822,"uid":363590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"頭先又聽到"},{"pid":"d3f32df21